Class GeneticPolynomialOptimizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.kasprowski.etcal.optimizer.AbstractOptimizer

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeneticOptimizer, Optimizer

    public class GeneticPolynomialOptimizer
extends PolynomialOptimizer
implements GeneticOptimizer
    For the given dataUnits tries to find the best masks (set of terms for 3rd degree polynomial) - uses genetic algorithm. getBest() method returns the best calibrator found so far.
    Author:
    pawel@kasprowski.pl
